20010.m_mBirthday: "Brought to life in a casket. Autumn, 1353."
20010.m_mCampText: "Perhaps... this is what I once longed for?"
20010.m_mFavorText: "I don't know if I like it, but I don't dislike this anticipation."

20020.m_mBirthday: "The Kalends of August, the day of harvest."
20020.m_mCampText: "This is... well, I'm not sure what to say. But thanks!"

20030.m_mBirthday: "The day when light and dark are equal."
20030.m_mCampText: "Amazing, how did you know I like this?"

20040.m_mBirthday: "The Ides of April, when green grass grows."
20040.m_mCampText: "I'm honored that you know my preferences so well."

20050.m_mBirthday: "The Kalends of November, the day of martyrs."
20050.m_mCampText: "This is one of my few indulgences outside of archery. You have my heartfelt gratitude."

20060.m_mBirthday: "The day of sea fall, the day of rebirth."
20060.m_mCampText: "How did you know I liked... Wait, have you been observing me?"

20070.m_mCampText: "Your insistence leaves me no choice but to accept."
20070.m_mFavorText: "I appreciate the sentiment, but I'm afraid it fails to pique my interest."

20080.m_mBirthday: "The day fireworks danced across the skies of Sapphire Isle."
20080.m_mCampText:
"Self: This is...
 Puppet: Where did you get this? We don't even have anything this nice!"
20080.m_mFavorText:
"Self: I'm sorry.
Puppet: She's actually thanking you!"

20090.m_mCampText: "I see. It appears to be a product of meticulous preparation. I shall grant it... a seventy."
20090.m_mFavorText: "How unexpected to find myself an invitee. I shall savor this evening."

20100.m_mBirthday: "The Nones of January, when the sky smoldered with flame."
20100.m_mCampText: "Looks like you've spent quite some time figuring out what I like."
20100.m_mFavorText: "No pain, no gain, but I'll gladly take the latter."

20110.m_mTipDescript: "Upon purchase, you will obtain the Vassal. If you already own the Vassal, you will instead receive its Spirit Siphon materials."

20120.m_mCampText: "How did you know? Just leave it there. I will enjoy it thoroughly."
20120.m_mFavorText: "Is this the appropriate time to express gratitude?"

20130.m_mCampText: "Did you... choose this specially for me? Only father ever gave me anything."

20140.m_mCampText: "Hear the whispers of the shadows? That's my gift to you."

20150.m_mCampText: "It's regrettable that I can't offer you anything in return in this state."
20150.m_mFavorText: "Speak. What do you want to gain?"

20160.m_mCampText: "I didn't expect you to remember what I like... Come, sit with me. Let's enjoy this together."
20160.m_mFavorText: "You've even chosen a style I like. How thoughtful of you."

20170.m_mBirthday: "The day of being adopted by Tris."

20180.m_mCampText: "I shall cherish this bond between us."
20180.m_mFavorText: "I can feel the sincerity in your heart."

20200.m_mCampText: "Oh! This is great stuff. I really appreciate it. Next time, let me treat you to some vegetables I grew myself!"
20200.m_mFavorText: "That's so considerate of you. You have my gratitude."

20210.m_mBirthday: "The morning when fierce winds carried a dirge."
20210.m_mCampText: "My, what an unexpected delight. It seems you're starting to catch on, little one."
20210.m_mFavorText: "Ooh, is it something fun to play with?"

20220.m_mCampText: "I should not accept this, but... Please allow me to briefly set aside my divine duties and relish this moment of tranquility."

20230.m_mTipDescript: "Upon purchase, you will obtain this Vassal. If you already own this Vassal, you will instead receive its Spirit Siphon materials."
20230.m_mBirthday: "The day of her death, and the start of her rebirth."
20230.m_mCampText: "The cards told me someone would bring me a gift today. Though it was foreseen, your presence still fills me with joy."

20270.m_mBirthday: "A night at the dock when ravens shadowed the sky."
20270.m_mCampText: "How did you know I… Wait, I should prepare something too…"

20280.m_mCampText: "Such a nostalgic aroma... Has it really been that long?"
20280.m_mFavorText: "I'll accept it for now. This, too, is part of the rules"

20290.m_mBirthday: "The Ides of April, when green grass grows."
20290.m_mCampText: "Perhaps this act of goodwill is what connects us in the future."

20300.m_mCampText: "Ah, this is a surprise. You've really gone out of your way for me."
20300.m_mFavorText: "As a token of gratitude, I will mend your wounds next time."

20310.m_mTipDescript: "Upon purchase, you will obtain the Vassal. If you already own the Vassal, you will instead receive its Spirit Siphon materials."
20310.m_mCampText: "So you've looked into my preferences... I will cherish this precious gift."
20310.m_mFavorText: "Is this my reward for completing my task?"

20330.m_mCampText: "The item in your hand reminds me of my weaker past self, but that time... is also the past I most wish to return to."
20330.m_mFavorText: "What a gentle audience you are... Then I shall accept your gift."

20340.m_mCampText: "I must strive to do even more for you in the days ahead."

20350.m_mCampText: "Think carefully now. Once this leaves your hand, you will share my sin."
20350.m_mFavorText: "What a hassle... Picking out a gift in return is no easy task, you know?"

20370.m_mBirthday: "The season lillies go in full bloom."
20370.m_mCampText: "I am a servant of God, why do my hands tremble...?"

20380.m_mCampText: "I am forever in your debt... Need anyone to disappear? It's on the house!"
20380.m_mFavorText: "Is this a bounty? Strange, I haven't taken any jobs recently."

20390.m_mBirthday: "Brought to life in a casket. Autumn, 1353."
20390.m_mCampText: "It seems the preparations are a tad too lavish."

20400.m_mBirthday: "The day blossoms flourish and branches bend with fruit."
20400.m_mCampText: "Though there's no time to rest, I will savor this thoughtful gift you have prepared for me!"

20420.m_mCampText: "I never thought I'd care about anything other than battle."
20420.m_mFavorText: "Why are you giving this to me?"

20430.m_mCampText: "So you've looked into my past, have you? How daring of you."
20430.m_mFavorText: "It's not exactly novel, but I can tell you put some thought into it. Thanks."

20450.m_mBirthday: "The day the sun met the horizon."
20450.m_mCampText: "The old me would have been thrilled... Thank you for reminding me of who I once was."

20470.m_mCampText: "Ah, this feeling... it's as if I've been transported back to the past. Thank you for allowing me to experience life once more."
20470.m_mFavorText: "Thank you for the things you have painstakingly prepared for me."

20480.m_mBirthday: "The day of sea fall, the day of rebirth."
20480.m_mCampText: "This gift seems to help me forget my past momentarily. Thank you. Maybe the nightmares will stop."
20480.m_mFavorText: "Since you prepared this for me, I'll accept it."

20490.m_mBirthday: "The first suit of armor was forged in the dead of winter, many centuries ago."
20490.m_mCampText: "This is too exquisite for me, but your kind intentions are duly noted!"

20500.m_mCampText: "If the town's children were still here, they would undoubtedly adore such a thing..."
20500.m_mFavorText: "This kindness, I shall cherish for a lifetime!"

20510.m_mCampText: "Can I really accept this? What am I saying... I need to find a way to repay you!"

20520.m_mBirthday: "During a certain autumn festival held by the family."
20520.m_mCampText: "For a commoner, you have quite the discerning eye."
20520.m_mFavorText: "You should know that such meager attempts at appeasement will hardly suffice."

20570.m_mCampText: "A pity I've cast aside my humanity... but for you, I suppose I'll make an exception."
20570.m_mFavorText: "I desire you more than this trivial offering."

20610.m_mBirthday: "The Ides of April, when green grass grows."
20610.m_mCampText: "Thank you… it reminds me of the time I spent with my companions."
20610.m_mFavorText: "Is this a token from your 'now'? Then I'll keep it close."

20620.m_mBirthday: "The first battle between the Bathory and the Ganelon."
20620.m_mCampText: "Please, no more. I fear I might grow accustomed to such warmth."
20620.m_mFavorText: "Is this... what it feels like to be cared for?"

20630.m_mBirthday: "The day of the Cartographer's Association's 2000th anniversary."
20630.m_mCampText: "Though I lack treasure... I offer something rarer— Tales from my cartographic expeditions! Care to hear them?"
20630.m_mFavorText: "A Bloodborn custom, perhaps? How fascinating... I must document this for my records."

20640.m_mBirthday: "The day when Tidewisps begin to bloom."

20650.m_mBirthday: "The day she was left at the monastery gate."
20650.m_mCampText: "Wow! This must be worth a fortune!"
20650.m_mFavorText: "This thing... I don't have to pay for it, do I?"

20660.m_mBirthday: "The Annual Fireworks Celebration in Sapphire Isle."
20660.m_mCampText:
"Bella: How did you know I liked these…?
Yakov: It must be fate! Two hearts, one mind, destined across space and time!"
20660.m_mFavorText:
"Bella: Thank you for your kindness, Mr. Nevernight of the Bathory family. Father taught me to always mind my manners.
Yakov: Wait, wait—does that mean Little Bella comes from a rich family?!"

20700.m_mCampText: "Impressive skills! Is this your secret to having so many Vassals?"
20700.m_mFavorText: "You thought this junk would impress me?"
